column1: The  prosecution  evidence  and  the  documents  marked  does  not  prove  that  the  accused-
appellant  had  acted  with  a  dishonest  intention  in  order  to  misappropriate  a  sum  of  Rs.
60,000/= which is due as stamp duty. The learned Trial Judge have failed to consider that the
charges against the accused-appellant are not proved beyond reasonable doubt.
